  <summary>&lt;p>Papirus - it's free and open source SVG-based icon theme for Linux with material and flat style.&lt;br />All elements have clear distinction and outlines. Also main feature - it's jucy colors tone.&lt;br />&lt;br />Papirus support hardcode-tray script:&lt;br />&lt;a href="https://github.com/bil-elmoussaoui/Hardcode-Tray/">https://github.com/bil-elmoussaoui/Hardcode-Tray/&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />Folder Color support:&lt;br />&lt;a href="http://foldercolor.tuxfamily.org">http://foldercolor.tuxfamily.org&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />Dolphin Folder Color support:&lt;br />&lt;a href="https://github.com/audoban/dolphin-folder-color">https://github.com/audoban/dolphin-folder-color&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />Papirus Folders script:&lt;br />&lt;a href="https://github.com/PapirusDevelopmentTeam/papirus-folders">https://github.com/PapirusDevelopmentTeam/papirus-folders&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />And KDE color scheme:&lt;br />&lt;a href="https://techbase.kde.org/Development/Tutorials/Plasma5/ThemeDetails#Colors">https://techbase.kde.org/Development/Tutorials/Plasma5/ThemeDetails#Colors&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />ANDROID Version available here:&lt;br />&lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1662847/">https://www.pling.com/p/1662847/&lt;/a>&lt;/p></summary>
